Summary: Bright like a big fire in sky at a distance
divs: Sighting DetailsHi there... I saw Jupiter tonight but not sure what I saw in the southwest sky. My wife and I were outside with the dogs and just when I was walking in the door I said to my wife "look at that!!!" It was big and bright in the southwest sky. Like a small moon with same intensity as ours. My wife called me a moron and told me it was Venus.
